displayChart.description: Your weekly update of the most popular tracks in Chandigarh, India.

labels.name: Sony Music Entertainment India Pvt. Ltd.

highlights.text: “Issue (Mudda Tere Ishq Da)” by Real Boss is the highest new entry on Top Songs Chandigarh at #79.
“Salute” by Arjan Dhillon is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Chandigarh, up 35 spots at #9.
Sidhu Moose Wala has the most spots on Top Songs Chandigarh. “Never Fold” is the highest at #13.
“On Top” by Karan Aujla has been on Top Songs Chandigarh the longest, at 13 weeks straight.
